data.description: Spectacular 2016 built beauty slightly lived in and in mint condition. Commencing from the impressive front street elevation accented by unique stone and masonry design makes this home ROCK. Step inside through oversized decorative door to breathtaking foyer featuring circular vaulted stepped ceiling and immediately feel the warmth and charm of gorgeous Hand Scraped wood floors extending throughout including study, hall, dining and family room.  Relax  and chill out with family or friends in your spacious den featuring towering ceiling, rows of windows, rock WBFP all overlooking football size yard. Den opens to an inspiring chef's kitchen with a dynamic island, butler's pantries and tons of cabinets.  Hideaway in the secluded and cozy owner's retreat with luxurious Texas size bath and spacious glass shower that accommodate two. Professional landscaped grounds supported with multi zoned watering system; unique 3 car covered parking; c patio and more. FRIENDS DO NOT MISS THIS ONE!
